      <section eId="sec_150_15">
        <num>150.15</num>
        <heading>Arson in the second degree</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_150_15__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>\nanother person who is not a participant in the crime is present in such\nbuilding or motor vehicle at the time, and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_150_15__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the defendant knows that\nfact or the circumstances are such as to render the presence of such a\nperson therein a reasonable possibility.\n  Arson in the second degree is a class B felony.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
